Tyrael: No need to go that way. They would identify us as predacons 
and destroy us. What's more, me and Naga are techno-organic. They will 
suspect something if they see either one of us. We will go straight to 
that point. (he showed a point past the end of the path) This is where 
the two ships had reported contact before they broke it. I do not know 
what has happened to any of then after that. We will go blindfolded 
after that point. We will have to maintain full alert at that moment 
and man all battle stations.
